text: Katharina Haecker (born 31 July 1992) is an Australian judoka. She competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the women's 63 kg event, in which she was eliminated in the second round by Miku Tashiro. ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Australian female judoka Category:Olympic judoka of Australia Category:Judoka at the 2016 Summer Olympics
